<p>
The <strong>SISYPHUS</strong> alignments are grouped into three categories:
<ul>
<li><a href="alignments.jsp?type=fragment">Fragment</a></li>
<li><a href="alignments.jsp?type=homologous">Homologous</a></li>
<li><a href="alignments.jsp?type=fold">Fold</a></li>
</ul>

please proceed to the <a href="categories.jsp">categories page</a> to learn more.
</p>


